#: ../../source/discussion.rst:2
msgid "discussion hub"
msgstr "discussion hub"

#: ../../source/discussion.rst:4
msgid "ISAT uses GitHub Discussions as the community discussion hub."
msgstr "ISAT은(는) GitHub 토론을 커뮤니티 토론 허브로 사용합니다."

#: ../../source/discussion.rst:6
msgid ""
"`ISAT community discussion hub "
"<https://github.com/yatengLG/ISAT_with_segment_anything/discussions>`_ is "
"the main place for users, contributors, and maintainers to exchange ideas, "
"ask for help, and discuss project developments."
msgstr ""
"`ISAT community discussion hub "
"<https://github.com/yatengLG/ISAT_with_segment_anything/discussions>`_ 은(는) "
"사용자, 기여자, 유지관리자가 아이디어를 교환하고, 도움을 요청하고, 프로젝트 개발에 대해 논의하는 주요 장소입니다."

#: ../../source/discussion.rst:8
msgid ""
"Welcome to post in the `ISAT community discussion hub "
"<https://github.com/yatengLG/ISAT_with_segment_anything/discussions>`_ !"
msgstr ""
"`ISAT community discussion hub "
"<https://github.com/yatengLG/ISAT_with_segment_anything/discussions>`_ 에 "
"게시하신 것을 환영합니다!"

#: ../../source/discussion.rst:12
msgid ""
"I will receive notifications for all posts in the discussion center as soon "
"as they are made. So don't worry about not getting feedback when you post in"
" the discussion area."
msgstr ""
"토론센터의 모든 게시물은 작성되는 즉시 알림을 받도록 하겠습니다. 따라서 토론 영역에 게시할 때 피드백을 받지 못할까 봐 걱정하지 "
"마세요."

#: ../../source/discussion.rst:15
msgid "1. Category sections"
msgstr "1. 카테고리 섹션"

#: ../../source/discussion.rst:17
msgid "Announcements - Updates from maintainers."
msgstr "공지 사항 - 관리자의 업데이트입니다."

#: ../../source/discussion.rst:18
msgid "General - Chat about anything and everything here."
msgstr "일반 - 여기에서 무엇이든 모든 것에 대해 채팅하세요."

#: ../../source/discussion.rst:19
msgid "Ideas - Share ideas for new features."
msgstr "아이디어 - 새로운 기능에 대한 아이디어를 공유하세요."

#: ../../source/discussion.rst:20
msgid "Q&A - Ask the community for help."
msgstr "Q&A - 커뮤니티에 도움을 요청하세요."

#: ../../source/discussion.rst:21
msgid "Show - Show off something you've made."
msgstr "보여주기 - 당신이 만든 것을 보여주세요."

#: ../../source/discussion.rst:22
msgid "Polls - Take a vote from the community."
msgstr "여론조사 - 커뮤니티에서 투표를 해보세요."

#: ../../source/discussion.rst:25
msgid "2. Discussion Etiquette"
msgstr "2. 토론 에티켓"

#: ../../source/discussion.rst:27
msgid "**What You Should Do**:"
msgstr "**해야 할 일**:"

#: ../../source/discussion.rst:29
msgid "Use descriptive titles."
msgstr "설명적인 제목을 사용하세요."

#: ../../source/discussion.rst:30
msgid "Post in the appropriate section."
msgstr "해당 섹션에 게시하세요."

#: ../../source/discussion.rst:31
msgid "Provide a detailed description of the problem."
msgstr "문제에 대한 자세한 설명을 제공하십시오."

#: ../../source/discussion.rst:32
msgid "Mark solutions as accepted."
msgstr "솔루션을 승인됨으로 표시하세요."

#: ../../source/discussion.rst:33
msgid "Thank those who offer help."
msgstr "도움을 주신 분들께 감사드립니다."

#: ../../source/discussion.rst:35
msgid "**What You Should Not Do**:"
msgstr "**하지 말아야 할 일**:"

#: ../../source/discussion.rst:37
msgid "Post repeatedly."
msgstr "반복해서 게시하세요."

#: ../../source/discussion.rst:38
msgid "Use offensive language."
msgstr "공격적인 언어를 사용하십시오."

#: ../../source/discussion.rst:39
msgid "Post irrelevant content."
msgstr "관련 없는 내용을 게시합니다."

#: ../../source/discussion.rst:40
msgid "Bump old posts (unless there is new information)."
msgstr "이전 게시물을 범프합니다(새로운 정보가 없는 한)."
